–’Щ@1e930429046ab37f5f2328feb036c76cd20f8ab692b0bc69b430b87a2937020aЩdTitle: title: move
Path: filters
Content:









``move``
[link: /commands/categories/filters.md] ’Щ@f3e36839e9bdd4dbb57a8f636925576c4edf2f98988c346d6e6850ea7d484fc9ЩGTitle: title: move
Path: Signature
Content:
``> move {flags} ...rest``
’Щ@9ca7c33dcae89f77ad4c628bf8c8de3bebb5fa93f1f2b092347292434fee6222Ъ%Title: title: move
Path: Flags
Content:
``--after {string}``
: The column that will precede the columns moved.
``--before {string}``
: The column that will be the next after the columns moved.
``--first``
: Makes the columns be the first ones.
``--last``
: Makes the columns be the last ones.
’Щ@0075aed1f170251156e26150ac3728f373b97cda212a51d3a23314a19354ed0dЩPTitle: title: move
Path: Parameters
Content:
``...rest``
: The columns to move.
’Щ@cdcefb5875c5e26490a38dc7c61c517d66db8d8f3a10ec39ba7283624421acb3Щ]Title: title: move
Path: Input/output types:
Content:
input
output
record
record
table
table
’Щ@b007910656866ce0b89fc4beb9a60ab593f2ec399c5bc36786229f2987e550e0ЪгTitle: title: move
Path: Examples
Content:
Move a column before the first column.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> [[name value index]; [foo a 1] [bar b 2] [baz c 3]] | move index --before name
в•ӯв”Җв”Җв”Җв”¬в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”¬в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв•®
в”Ӯ # в”Ӯ name в”Ӯ value в”Ӯ
в”ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”јв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”јв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Ө
в”Ӯ 1 в”Ӯ foo  в”Ӯ a     в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ 2 в”Ӯ bar  в”Ӯ b     в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ 3 в”Ӯ baz  в”Ӯ c     в”Ӯ
в•°в”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҙв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҙв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв•Ҝ


```
Move multiple columns after the last column and reorder them.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> [[name value index]; [foo a 1] [bar b 2] [baz c 3]] | move value name --after index
в•ӯв”Җв”Җв”Җв”¬в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”¬в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв•®
в”Ӯ # в”Ӯ value в”Ӯ name в”Ӯ
в”ңв”Җв”Җв”Җв”јв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”јв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Ө
в”Ӯ 1 в”Ӯ a     в”Ӯ foo  в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ 2 в”Ӯ b     в”Ӯ bar  в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ 3 в”Ӯ c     в”Ӯ baz  в”Ӯ
в•°в”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҙв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҙв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв•Ҝ


```
Move columns of a record.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> { name: foo, value: a, index: 1 } | move name --before index
в•ӯв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”¬в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв•®
в”Ӯ value в”Ӯ a   в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ name  в”Ӯ foo в”Ӯ
в”Ӯ index в”Ӯ 1   в”Ӯ
в•°в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”ҙв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв•Ҝ

```
